{"tid":1789164,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"廣東茂名再傳示威","createTime":"2019-12-19T09:03:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T09:11:58.000Z","uid":323232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bfb053674fa274ea81c1c0dc58a2d064ff51f23f","tid":1789164,"uid":323232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T09:03:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/INzTZY63HHw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FINzTZY63HHw&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfEBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=4f330991\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/INzTZY63HHw</a><br />\n【播揚抗爭者模仿港人向公安投汽油彈】 廣東茂名文樓鎮市民上月底成功阻止政府建火葬場，在距離文樓鎮27公裏的播揚鎮，又傳出當地政府計劃將火葬場遷往當地，周壹開始當地逾萬人上街示威，武警到場動用催淚彈鎮壓。網絡視頻看到，抗爭者也學了香港同道，向公安局投擲汽油彈。"},{"pid":"f07c659ce4c55e40745d061acb0c9e07f6907a40","tid":1789164,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T09:11:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">12.22  愛丁堡<br />\n12.21  721五個月 <br />\n12.24 和你shop<br />\n12.24  夜晚尖咀見<br />\n12.31  和你拖<br />\n2020.1.1元旦大遊行</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sEffSro.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsEffSro.jpg&h=99a1f162&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VBcxEME.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVBcxEME.jpg&h=7ab8f960&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NKLvrrF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNKLvrrF.jpg&h=653d2ffc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mY6iAj1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmY6iAj1.jpg&h=c159792d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5tVOXym.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5tVOXym.jpg&h=2b5d9c8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9uVGNZR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9uVGNZR.